cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.SY. 

The paper is about a library for optimizing deep learning hyper-parameters, which is a common problem in machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision), as these fields heavily rely on deep learning. The paper also mentions network configuration, which suggests cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as a possible category. Finally, the library can be used for system optimization, which could fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control).
